                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210606-181-off1043 t18210606-181-crimeloc1046"></join>. On the 27th of April, about half-past nine o'clock at night, I saw the prisoner come inside the door, and take this print; I followed him up Cannon-street, and saw him drop it about thirty yards from the door; I followed, and took him; the print was brought in by a stranger.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I heard the cry, and ran in pursuit, a man laid hold of me - several were running before me.</p>
